high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the kitchen counter right of the oven
Pick up the large golden spoon from the counter
Turn right and walk up to the kitchen sink
Rinse the spoon under running water in the sink then remove it
Turn left and walk a few feet over to the counter where the toaster is
Put the spoon down on the counter in front of the toaster
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned spoon on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn right, turn right, walk toward sink, turn left, walk to counter.
Turn right, turn right, walk to sink, turn left to face sink.
Put ladle in sink, wash ladle.
Take ladle from sink, turn left walk to counter beside sink, turn to face counter.
anns.task_desc: Place clean ladle on counter in front of toaster.

high_descs: Go past the sink to the counter by the stove.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Put the ladle in the sink and rinse it off.
Take the ladle to the counter by the toaster.
Set the ladle on the counter in front of the toaster to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the counter.
